      <li>Str:+1, End:+1, Ag:+0, Spd:-1, Per:+1</li>
    </list>
  </archetypeprimaryabilities>
  <archetypeinitialabilities>
    <p>
      All Confessor Militants start with the following skills: Hammer Strike II,
      Shield Block II, Aquilonian II, Etiquette II [Church of Mithras], Augury I,
      Litany of Redemption, Light of Mithras I, Blessed Arms of Mithras I, Turn Undead I,
      Merovingian IV.
    </p>

    <p>
    </p>
      
